<h2>6. Security &amp; Scalability (الأمان والتوسع)</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Security / الأمان:</strong> Strict foreign key constraints prevent orphan records. Endpoints must validate ownership before interacting with ticket specific records.</li>
<li><strong>Scalability / التوسع:</strong> Ticket Threads and Activities tables are expected to grow rapidly. Implement table partitioning by year.</li>
</ul>

